OL,3,CDon't swim in these 'bathing waters',
OL,4,Cwarn experts
OL,6,FDespite there being 13 new bathing
OL,7,Fsites, dozens aren't suitable for
OL,8,Fswimming due to their high pollution
OL,9,Flevels. Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,10,Freports from the beach in Lyme Regis
OL,12,FAs the official outdoor swimming
OL,13,Fseason gets underway, experts and
OL,14,Fcampaigners are warning that dozens of
OL,15,F"bathing waters" are not fit to swim
OL,16,Fin.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@PO]
