OL,3,CDon't swim in these 'bathing waters',
OL,4,Cwarn experts
OL,6,FITV News visited one beach designated
OL,7,Fas an official "bathing water"
OL,8,Flocation, where water quality is so
OL,9,Fpoor that swimming is strongly
OL,10,Fdiscouraged.
OL,12,FChurch Cliff beach in Lyme Regis has a
OL,13,Fsign saying "swimming not advised",
OL,14,Fthe reason given is "due to poor
OL,15,Fclassification given to this beach
OL,16,Ffrom last year's sampling."
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@^O]uD@MOUuD@bO]vD@UOUxD@[O]
