OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778904285
OL,3,CDon't swim in these 'bathing waters',
OL,4,Cwarn experts
OL,6,FWe spoke to Lyme Regis sea swimmer
OL,7,FBeverley Glock, "We need to know that
OL,8,Fit's going to be safe, that we're not
OL,9,Fgoing to be ill. If we can't go in
OL,10,Fbecause there's been a sewage dump,
OL,11,Fthen our day is completely
OL,12,Fruined...our week is ruined. It's even
OL,13,Fworse if one of us is poorly."
OL,15,FThe government told us "four in five
OL,16,Fbathing sites are rated as either
OL,17,Fexcellent or good."
OL,26,@oD@QOUwD@XOUyD@SO]
