OL,3,CDon't swim in these 'bathing waters',
OL,4,Cwarn experts
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid it's committed to improving water
OL,8,Fquality and that bathing sites "will
OL,9,Fbe rigorously and regularly
OL,10,Ftested...meaning swimmers are better
OL,11,Finformed about water quality and can
OL,12,Fswim with greater confidence".
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
